Quando eu soube?

469
00:36:55,257 --> 00:36:56,657
Do quê?

470
00:36:57,137 --> 00:36:58,537
Que eu era...

471
00:36:58,937 --> 00:37:00,337
o Justiça Encapuzada.

472
